channel.description:
[center][IMG]http://i.imgur.com/CtaMB.gif[/img]
[url=http://www.Rune-Soft.co.cc]Click here If your a bad ass.[/url]
Hello MoparScape,
I've been working on this base for 4-5 days and I thought'd I'd share the progress with you guys. The reason I started developing this server was because I'm tired of seeing the same shit everywhere I want something new and unique but at the same time I want it to be old school. Before you even begin thinking of playing, no we do not have new items this is a 377 server with the exception of only a few items which allows the server to stay alive.
[b]Forum Features:[/b]
• Reliable and fast web hosting. • Updated frequently. • Easy to use. • Clean and tidy.
I'm not going to name a bunch of features that aren't true, Here are some main things.
• Near perfect combat. • Near perfect slayer. • Great training facilities! • Various PKing teleports! • Realistic economy. • Protect item interface. • All four godwars bosses.
Media.
